                            {
                                "kind": "label-md",
                                "display": {
                                    "en": "This membership form covers information that our union treats as confidential. It will be held securely and is only used for union purposes. For more information on how we use your information please see our [Privacy Policy](/page/about/privacy). \n\nI agree to join the Independent Workers' Union of Great Britain (IWGB) and authorise IWGB to collect my membership fees by Direct Debit. \n\nI understand that, in joining the union, I agree to the union's [constitution](/page/secret/constitution) and rules and the union's policies. I understand that the constitution, rules and policies may be amended from time to time."
